0.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/Boyrun-Regular.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=792405807634160&amp;ev=PageView&amp;noscript=1" as="image" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/","name":"Meetup","logo":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/next/images/general/m_redesign_630x630.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/meetup/","https://twitter.com/Meetup/","https://www.youtube.com/meetup","https://www.instagram.com/meetup/"]}</script><meta name="description" content="Welcome to Auckland AWS Tools and Programming meetup group!We&#x27;re a group of developers, programmers, and other tech professionals passionate about AWS technology. We want to enable the opportunity for our community to come together to learn, discuss and share knowledge about AWS tools and best pract" data-next-head=""/><meta property="fb:app_id" content="2403839689" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:type" content="article" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:title" content="Auckland AWS Tools and Programming | Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:description" content="Welcome to Auckland AWS Tools and Programming meetup group!We&#x27;re a group of developers, programmers, and other tech professionals passionate about AWS technology. We want to enable the opportunity for our community to come together to learn, discuss and share knowledge about AWS tools and best pract" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/f/1/600_526698161.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:package" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_store_id" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:should_fallback" content="true" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:site" content="@meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/f/1/600_526698161.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:description" content="Welcome to Auckland AWS Tools and Programming meetup group!We&#x27;re a group of developers, programmers, and other tech professionals passionate about AWS technology. We want to enable the opportunity for our community to come together to learn, discuss and share knowledge about AWS tools and best pract" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:iphone" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:ipad" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:ipad" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:googleplay" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:googleplay" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Event","name":"Agentic AI Evaluation on Bedrock: Lessons from Pushpay's Journey","url":"https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/events/315277156/","description":"Hello everyone,\n\nWe're excited to invite you to the **Auckland AWS Tools and Programming meetup**!\n\nThis month, we are diving deep into the realities of moving AI from a cool demo to a production-ready system. We are thrilled to host two fantastic co-speakers: **[Roger Wang](https://www.linkedin.com/in/roger-nz/)** (Senior Solutions Architect @ AWS) and **[Saurabh Gupta](https://www.linkedin.com/in/nzsaurabh/)** (Pushpay).\n\nWe are gathering once again at the *Pushpay office in the CBD*—looking forward to seeing you all there!\n\n🚨 **Action Required:** To help us streamline building security and sort out the catering (including dietary requirements), please make sure to pre-register before arriving: 👉 **[Pre-register for Venue Check-In Here](https://eventspaces.app/e/build-reliable-agentic-ai-solution-learn-from-pushpay-s-journey-on-agentic-ai-evaluation-f9b80e/register)**\n\n⚠️ *Important Day Change: Please note that we are meeting on a Tuesday this month instead of our usual Thursday slot!*\n\n**🎤 The Lineup**\n**Roger Wang (AWS) & Saurabh Gupta (Pushpay)**\n\n* **Title:** Breaking Through the 65% Ceiling: How Pushpay Engineered a 95% Accurate Production AI Agent\n* **Description:** Agentic AI plateaus fast once you move beyond demos. Pushpay's natural language search agent hit a \\~65% accuracy ceiling before the team built a structured evaluation framework to break through it.\nRoger and Saurabh will walk through Pushpay's real-world journey: building the agent on **Amazon Bedrock**, why accuracy stalled, and the engineering techniques that pushed it to 95%. They will share practical takeaways including constructing a 300+ query golden dataset, automating measurement with LLM-as-a-Judge, and applying domain-specific prompt engineering on Bedrock. No hype—just real numbers, a real production system, and actionable insights for anyone building or operating agents.\n\n**📍 Venue & Day Reminder**\n\n* Venue: We are back at the Pushpay office in the Auckland CBD again this month! You can find the address details below.\n* Day Change: Don't forget, we are meeting on Tuesday this time around.\n\n**📅 Event Details**\n\n* When: 5:00 pm on Tuesday, 23rd June 2026 (Note the day change!)\n* Where: Pushpay Office, Level 19, 48 Shortland Street, Auckland\n\n**⏰ Agenda**\n\n* 5:00 pm - Welcome & Networking\n* 5:30 pm - Presentation & Deep Dive\n* 6:30 pm - Q&A, Announcements, & Networking\n\nThis event is proudly supported by **Pushpay**, **Mantel Group**, and **AWS**.\nWe look forward to seeing you there!\n**– The Auckland AWS Tools and Programming Team**\n\n***Code of Conduct***\n*Auckland AWS Tools and Programming is committed to providing a friendly and welcoming space for everyone who attends our meetup events, regardless of gender, gender identity and expression, age, sexual orientation, disability, physical appearance, body size, race, ethnicity, religion (or lack thereof), or technology choices. Any form of harassment, racism, misogyny, or xenophobia is unacceptable. Participants violating these rules will be invited to leave the meetup.*","startDate":"2026-06-23T05:00:00.000Z","endDate":"2026-06-23T07:00:00.000Z","eventStatus":"https://schema.org/EventScheduled","image":"","eventAttendanceMode":"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode","location":{"@type":"Place","name":"Pushpay Office","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Auckland","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"nz","streetAddress":"Level 19, Vero Centre, 48 Shortland Street, Auckland CBD, Auckland"}},"organizer":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Auckland AWS Tools and Programming","url":"https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/"},"performer":"Auckland AWS Tools and Programming"}]</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/","name":"Auckland AWS Tools and Programming","image":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/f/1/600_526698161.webp","foundingDate":"2022-12-06T10:22:08.000Z","address":{"location":{"@type":"Place","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Auckland","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"nz"}}},"sameAs":["https://www.youtube.com/@auckland-aws-tools-meetup"]}</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@id":"https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/","name":"Auckland AWS Tools and Programming"}}]}</script><meta property="geo.position" content="-36.85;174.76" data-next-head=""/><meta property="geo.placename" content="Auckland" data-next-head=""/><meta property="geo.region" content="nz" data-next-head=""/><link rel="canonical" href="https://www.meetup.com/auckland-aws-tools-meetup/" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://secure-content.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://secure-content.meetupstatic.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preconnect" href="https://www.googletagmanager.com" data-next-head=""/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://www.googletagmanager.com" data-next-head=""/><title data-next-head="">Auckland AWS Tools and Programming | Meetup</title><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/6/f/1/clean_526698161.webp" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/c/0/2/8/highres_534769192.jpeg" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/4/b/8/3/highres_534319331.jpeg" as="image" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://secure.me